Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.32,0:00:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heroes are powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.20,0:00:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heroes are lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.33,0:00:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and they walk off alone in the final scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.63,0:00:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He was just like that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.97,0:00:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My hero was just like that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.23,0:00:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.94,0:00:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He was disqualified the\Ninstant he stopped playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.32,0:00:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Only scattered applause.\NA confused audience...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.57,0:00:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, why not? Only one person matters to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.66,0:00:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will it reach her?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.04,0:00:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hope it reaches her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.81,0:02:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There will now be an intermission.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.36,0:02:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A competition is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.48,0:02:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A competition is a\Nsacred garden of music.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.49,0:02:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Under no circumstances is it\N a place to find yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still the same prickly\Nold geezer, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.21,0:03:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And he's escalated with old age.\NGod help us. Hey, Mr. Mediocre!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.93,0:03:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seto-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's Hiroko-san, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.60,0:03:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You cut your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For a second, I didn't recognize you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, a woman changes her\N'do every time she finds a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.32,0:03:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, it's been two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.53,0:03:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the stunner?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow I think I've seen her before...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.79,0:03:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Kousei, keeping her from\Nme. I thought you were my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's that lady who was\Nalways with Kousei's mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.21,0:03:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroko Seto. She's Japan's leading pianist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hello, Koharu-chan. Do you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since she was classmates with\NArima-kun's mother, Saki Arima, in college,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.01,0:03:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it makes sense that they\Nwould know each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.81,0:04:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here, there are all these Kouseis\Nthat I know nothing about.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.07,0:04:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Huh? Hiroko-san,\Neveryone's staring!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.20,0:04:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, Hiroko. Hold him, will you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.99,0:04:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? How do I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Support his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gently, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he adorable?\NHis name is Kousei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.63,0:04:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to turn\Nhim into a pianist?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not if I can help it. That's such a\Ndemanding job. He's my treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.97,0:04:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to turn him into a pianist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.18,0:04:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.93,0:04:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei's a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.31,0:04:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...me. Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.64,0:04:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kousei. I'm sorry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.19,0:04:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry. I'm sorry...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.73,0:04:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You got so big, Kousei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.20,0:04:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You smell like cigarettes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.37,0:05:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, our nostalgic\Nreunion is over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.37,0:05:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your friends are glaring at\Nus with the scariest faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops! Busted!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.67,0:05:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to stay for the results, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.17,0:05:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'm out of the running anyway,\Nand I'm not here for results.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.10,0:05:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the way you bombed\Nwas all kinds of extraordinary!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.51,0:05:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's really harsh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.10,0:05:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, you should be\Nthere when the results go up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.57,0:05:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, which one is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.63,0:05:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The girl with the long hair?\N Or with the short hair? Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.24,0:05:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Which is the girl you're in love with?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.82,0:05:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.57,0:05:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.62,0:05:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,lying to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.87,0:05:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your piano was singing it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.16,0:05:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saying, "I love you..."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.75,0:05:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you unaware? Or are\Nyou pretending not to notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.42,0:05:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your hidden emotions.\NThe you that you never knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.34,0:05:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The piano will drag out\Neverything in your youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.14,0:05:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brace yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.22,0:06:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, see you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.89,0:06:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not like that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.02,0:06:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is just gratitude...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.44,0:06:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After all, she's...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.19,0:06:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's the girl who likes my best\Nfriend. And I'm Friend A, after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.54,0:06:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We will now post the names of those who\Ncleared the first round of the preliminaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.17,0:06:29.21,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maiho Music Competition\NQualifiers\NPianists\NTakeshi Aiza
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.63,0:06:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Found my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.79,0:06:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.46,0:06:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Arima-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.09,0:06:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So Arima's name isn't listed, after all...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.10,0:06:43.10,MSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emi Igawa
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Heroes don't succumb. Heroes don't crumble.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.57,0:06:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just as expected. I stopped\Nplaying midway, after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.86,0:06:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.36,0:07:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I did it! There's my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.24,0:07:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What, I didn't make it again this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.95,0:07:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna work hard towards\N next year's competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And this was my last chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.79,0:07:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so bitter...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.63,0:07:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so bitter... So bitter...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.51,0:07:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Takeshi...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.47,0:07:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What was up with that performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.93,0:07:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What have you been doing all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My goal is Kousei Arima.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.48,0:07:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flip-flopping between\Nplaying styles like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.23,0:07:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Turning in such a train\Nwreck of a performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.65,0:07:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where did the almighty Arima go?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.24,0:07:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The lonely pianist, my\Nhero - where did he go?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.58,0:07:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My hero is made of super alloy...\Nmy hero never loses!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.46,0:07:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You knew that if you stopped playing,\Nyou wouldn't make it past the prelims.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.84,0:07:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So why...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.00,0:07:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why do you have that look on your face?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.51,0:08:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Heroes always win, no matter what.\NThis is like... it's like you're actually human.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.68,0:08:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So it was a train wreck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.85,0:08:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then that means I turned in\Nanother sloppy performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.11,0:08:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rumor has it that Arima\Ncan't hear the notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.82,0:08:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He really can't hear the notes...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.12,0:08:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I wasn't slacking at all. I practiced\Ntill I passed out. I gave my all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.12,0:08:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're just you, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.50,0:08:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And if I still turned in a sloppy\Nperformance after all that, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.59,0:08:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's who I am now. It's the current\Nme, playing with everything I've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.43,0:08:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mozart said, "Go on a journey."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.19,0:08:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have no idea what lies ahead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.02,0:08:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I've taken the first steps.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.65,0:09:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're still in the middle of our journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.21,0:09:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.92,0:09:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm a musician, just like you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.13,0:09:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why I'm moving on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.85,0:09:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That guy's changed, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.10,0:09:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bet he's found it. A reason to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.73,0:09:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His playing...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.86,0:09:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For just an instant, you could see\Na mischievous child peering out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.62,0:09:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Say something to him, Tsubaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.95,0:09:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's depressed because he lost for\Nthe first time ever, that Kousei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.71,0:09:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You go talk to him! You're a man, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.46,0:10:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine, okay? I'm totally cool with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.59,0:10:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.02,0:10:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A competition is a sacred garden of music.\NIt's not a place to find yourself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What was up with that performance?\NWhat have you been doing all this time?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.03,0:10:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.08,0:10:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A robot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.18,0:10:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Human Metronome.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.79,0:10:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His mother's puppet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.41,0:10:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I'm a robot... If I'm a puppet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm so bitter!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.67,0:10:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I missed my chance at becoming a star.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.39,0:10:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Kousei?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.31,0:10:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:11:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's up with these emotions?\NSomething's moving me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.07,0:11:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Run!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.07,0:11:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Run!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.91,0:11:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right. I'm the same as you, Tsubaki, Watari.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm a person, just like you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.21,0:11:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei's out of his mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.96,0:11:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.13,0:11:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Kaori.\NHow was he? Arima-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.76,0:11:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He was extremely entertaining!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.39,0:11:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that comment?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.39,0:11:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Details later!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.02,0:11:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's a letter here for you, Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.14,0:11:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.69,0:11:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get changed.\NI'm drenched with sweat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.67,0:12:01.00,SSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Towa Music Competition
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.85,0:12:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.65,0:12:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.53,0:12:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you up? You've been resurrected!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.15,0:12:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zombie? Zombie?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.07,0:12:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Seto-san? Good morning.\N What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.25,0:12:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't pick up no matter\Nhow many times I called you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.00,0:12:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm here out of\Nworry, you little punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.67,0:12:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, aren't those the clothes\Nyou were wearing yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.42,0:12:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Would it kill you to\Ntake a bath? The filth!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.47,0:12:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to give you a\Nwash just like old times?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.43,0:12:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! I'll wash up myself. And\NI'll take my clothes off myself, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.93,0:12:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh! Growing up\Non me, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.86,0:13:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You were playing all night,\Nuntil you passed out, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.57,0:13:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hiro-chan!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.83,0:13:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look at you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.37,0:13:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Boys will be boys, after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.71,0:13:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go. Se- Hiroko-san,\Nyou take your coffee black, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.38,0:13:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hold it where it's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.97,0:13:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is Takahiko-san still away on business?\NEver the free range parent, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.85,0:13:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Will milk be okay for you, Koharu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.89,0:13:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it has been two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.02,0:13:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, I never thought\Nyou'd take up the piano again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.82,0:13:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Neither did I.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.28,0:13:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So what made you turn to the piano again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.43,0:14:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.81,0:14:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nein! There'll be no breaks for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.94,0:14:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The day before yesterday, an invitation\Nfrom the Towa Hall office arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.11,0:14:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,An invitation?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.94,0:14:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Towa Hall... as in that competition\Nyou and Kousei played in?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that by any chance... the gala concert?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.82,0:14:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ja!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.83,0:14:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Gala concert" refers to
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.54,0:14:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,a special performance held\Nto commemorate something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.25,0:14:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In this case, it's a recital to mark\Nthe heights achieved by the winners
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and other top performers at\Nthe Towa Music Competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, so if it were a sport, it\Nwould be like an exhibition match?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.80,0:15:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Full marks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.06,0:15:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And as the promoters' choice,\Nwe've been invited.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.52,0:15:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Me, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.81,0:15:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.44,0:15:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So the almighty\Nduo is back in business!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.07,0:15:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.91,0:15:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.42,0:15:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is our song for the\Ngala concert set?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.07,0:15:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.55,0:15:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to do this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.59,0:15:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.93,0:15:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kreisler's Liebesleid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.81,0:15:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Love's Sorrow...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.06,0:15:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kousei...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.48,0:15:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're playing this at the gala?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.52,0:15:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, you'd do something\Nmore major, more showy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.44,0:15:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This one's really subdued.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.78,0:15:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay, that's okay. We're\Njust the throw-ins, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.61,0:16:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way anyone else\Nwill be playing this song,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.53,0:16:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and we're bound to stand out\Nmore if we play something chill.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.08,0:16:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These galas are all about\Nstanding out, don't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.20,0:16:09.21,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,F Kreisler\NLove's Sorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.83,0:16:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do something else.\NSomething cooler!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.35,0:16:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.06,0:16:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As someone who dropped you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.52,0:16:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't deserve to be a violinist. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please bear with me for just a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.37,0:16:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That small back. So tiny, she looks like\Nshe'll crumble away at my touch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.75,0:16:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.46,0:16:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.34,0:17:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What made you\Nturn to the piano?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.80,0:17:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One day in April,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.89,0:17:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I met a really weird violinist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.14,0:17:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Totally outrageous. Self-righteous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.44,0:17:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But the smile she shows to\Npeople she likes is angelic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.23,0:17:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I got onstage after she kicked,\Npunched, and dragged me up there...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.15,0:17:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On that familiar stage, I saw a\Nsight that I'd never seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.37,0:17:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see that sight again\Nwith my own eyes one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.62,0:17:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's what made me think...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.29,0:17:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That I'd like to become a really weird pianist!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.84,0:17:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.09,0:17:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch. Ouch...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.05,0:17:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then who else but me\Nto serve as your guardian?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.14,0:17:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's with that horrified reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.01,0:17:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.08,0:18:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please. Teach me to play the piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.59,0:18:18.88,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Doryo Bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.13,0:18:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.13,0:18:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,will you start taking this seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am. We played together for the first time.\NThat's about what you should expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.76,0:18:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really into...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.47,0:18:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.19,0:18:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're pretty, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.57,0:18:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you squash it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.74,0:18:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So ephemeral and weak. But\Nit's shining with all its might.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.79,0:18:59.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thump, thump, like a heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.25,0:19:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the light of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.43,0:19:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, testing, testing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.52,0:19:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How was it? Your\Nfirst competition in ages?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.65,0:19:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know what,\NI felt it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.36,0:19:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That everyone has something\Ndeep in their hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.83,0:19:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For some it might be hostility.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aspiration, hopes. The\Ndesire to show off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.17,0:19:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To think, "Let it reach them."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.71,0:19:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feelings for my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.84,0:19:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We all had our personal emotions to lean on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.55,0:19:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's not possible for someone to\Nget up on stage in an innocent state.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.26,0:19:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.93,0:19:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What did you have in your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.98,0:20:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What did you lean on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.66,0:20:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.14,0:20:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm... going on a journey.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.06,0:20:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The applause raining down.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.31,0:20:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pursuing that moment when\Nmy music reached them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.40,0:20:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pursuing that sight of\Nher with her back to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.07,0:20:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until one day, for sure,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.62,0:20:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've pulled even with her...\N until that day comes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.25,0:21:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.34,0:21:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"You know, I’m not always\Ngoing to be around to help you..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.01,0:21:20.02,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Light of Life
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.93,0:21:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...Charlie Brown.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.95,0:22:38.87,Next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 12\NTwinkle Little Star
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.02,0:22:55.02,BTSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Watch Again Next Week!
